headline: Jack Henry and Moov to Implement Mastercard Move to Enable Fast, Seamless Domestic Payments
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced today an extended collaboration with Mastercard to offer Mastercard Move, Mastercard's portfolio of money transfer solutions, through Jack Henry Rapid Transfers™, a cloud-native service that will enable near-real time* money movement. This includes account funding and a variety of payment use cases in the United States via the Mastercard network.
